d to the realization of various new self-induced nonreciprocal\nnanophotonic configurations, such as integrated ultrafast switches, ultrathin\nprotective coatings, and asymmetric directional imaging devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Dec 2022 19:34:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-22"}
