on of 1 mm x 1 mm, a total scan time of 3 minutes,\na temperature resolution of 6 K, and an uncertainty in hydration within 15%.\nThe demonstrated mapping can be generalized for imaging exchange membranes of\nany fuel cells or flow batteries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Dec 2022 20:37:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 1 Jan 2023 13:15:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 7 Jan 2023 14:57:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-10"}
