 it means that an increasing number of evanescent eigenmodes\nemerge when the domain size increases. We conclude that sausage perturbations\nremain difficult to detect even for the waveguide formulated here.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 01:26:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-08"}
