relationship between the percentage decrease and maximum hourly decrease is\nalso in agreement with previous studies, and follows trends relating to the\nexpansion of ICMEs as they propagate through the heliosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 02:03:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-08"}
