+$.m$^{-2}$.s$^{-1}$. The present set of results should be used to\nconstrain the development of He retention and He bubbles growth models based on\nab initio quantities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 12:19:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-07"}
